Jane Seymour (Canadian actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jane_Seymour_(Canadian_actress) 0 Jane Seymour (born Marjorie Seymour Fitz-patrick; March 24, 1893 – January 30, 1956) was a Canadian-American film and television actress known for her performance in films including Tom, Dick and Harry (1941) and for roles in several TV series.
